<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2018—Subsec. (a). <ref href="/us/pl/115/392/s11/2/A">Pub. L. 115–392, § 11(2)(A)</ref>, substituted “3 times” for “twice”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Subsec. (b)(1)(B). <ref href="/us/pl/115/392/s11/2/B">Pub. L. 115–392, § 11(2)(B)</ref>, substituted “subparagraph (A)” for “paragraph (1)”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2008—Subsec. (b)(1)(A). <ref href="/us/pl/110/457">Pub. L. 110–457</ref> substituted “chapter 110, or section 1591” for “or chapter 110”.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2003—Subsec. (a). <ref href="/us/pl/108/21">Pub. L. 108–21</ref> inserted “, unless section 3559(e) applies” before period at end.</p>
